visibility: SANDBOX
license: OFL
category: serif
subsets: menu,latin,latin-ext

family: Ledger

designer: Denis Masharov

approved: true
description: <p>The austere and concise \
  personality and flexibility make it a \
  real multiple-purpose typeface. The letter \
  forms are distinguished by a large x-height, \
  sufficient stroke contrast, robust but \
  elegant wedge-like serifs and terminals. \
  These features have been specially designed \
  to reach maximum of quality and readability \
  when used in unfavorable print and display \
  processes - such as in newspapers, laser \
  printed documents and on low resolution \
  screens. The typeface can be qualified as \
  matched to modern trends of type design \
  and of enhanced legibility. These \
  characteristics provide an undeniable \
  distinction to the typeface, making it \
  suitable for editorial use in newspapers \
  and magazines, corporate ID, advertising \
  and display typography.</p>

font.Ledger-Regular.ttf.style: normal
font.Ledger-Regular.ttf.weight: 400

